data.description: This beautiful home is conveniently located on the new area of the upper east side. Some of the included amenities are: granite countertops, window shutters, ceramic tile flooring with the look of wood planks, spacious backyard, extra side space, gourmet style kitchen, backyard landscaping plus many more! This floorplan is designed to entertain friends and family. Check it out today before this opportunity is gone!
